Name: quran
Description: Quran tools (ayahs, surahs, tafsir: Jalalayn, Kanzul Iman).
Version: 1.0

Commands:
- quran_get_ayah
  Get a single ayah.
  Parameters:
  - surah (integer, required)
  - ayah (integer, required)
  - edition (string, optional)

- quran_get_surah
  Get a full surah.
  Parameters:
  - surah (integer, required)
  - edition (string, optional)

- quran_get_tafsir
  Get tafsir for an ayah (Jalalayn / Kanzul Iman).
  Parameters:
  - surah (integer, required)
  - ayah (integer, required)
  - tafsir (string, optional): jalalayn|kanzuliman|custom

- quran_search
  Search Quran text (Quran.com API).
  Parameters:
  - query (string, required)
  - language (string, optional)
  - page (integer, optional)
  - per_page (integer, optional)

- quran_get_surah_list
  Get list of all surahs.

Data:
- Uses local JSON datasets under app/database/quran/*.json
